   July 11: Actress Sela Ward (''Once and Again'') is 44. Singer
Peter Murphy of Bauhaus is 43. Musician Richie Sambora of Bon Jovi
is 41. Singer Suzanne Vega is 41. Actor Michael Rosenbaum (''Zoe'')
is 28. Rapper Lil' Kim is 25.
