   July 12: Actor-comedian Bill Cosby is 63. Singer-musician
Christine McVie of Fleetwood Mac is 57. Musician Dan Murphy of Soul
Asylum is 38. Actress Lisa Nicole Carson (''Ally McBeal'') is 31.
Rapper Magoo is 27. Singer Tracie Spencer is 24. Actor Topher Grace
(''That '70s Show'') is 22. Actor Erik Per Sullivan (''Malcolm in
the Middle'') is 9.
