   July 13: Actor Patrick Stewart is 60. Singer-musician Roger
McGuinn of the Byrds is 58. Actor Harrison Ford is 58.
Actor-comedian Cheech Marin (''Nash Bridges'') is 54. Country
singer Louise Mandrell is 46. Director Cameron Crowe is 43. Singer
