<P>
   ''We'll just follow him wherever we can,'' said 13-year-old
Amanda Downes, who rushed the stage with a 12-year-old friend.
</P>
<P>
   When he finally appeared, Bass greeted the crowd, introduced
Edwards, waved and left the stage. It lasted 26 seconds.
</P>
<P>
   ''I think I saw the back of his head!'' shrieked Danielle
Marchione, 18.
