<HEADLINE> Liberty 62, Fire 45  </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
   NEW YORK (AP) -- Vickie Johnson and Becky Hammon scored 15 points
apiece as the New York Liberty beat the expansion Portland Fire
62-45 on Wednesday night.
</P>
