(8-9), who snapped a two-game losing streak. Sophia Witherspoon led
the Fire (4-11) with nine points and Sylvia Crawley added eight.
</P>
<P>
   New York had a season-high 14 steals, including five from
Phillips, who had her seventh double-double.
</P>
